title: SAP HANA Replication Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/sap
license: GPL
distribution: heinlein
description:
 This check monitors the replication status of SAP HANA. It uses data provided by the {sap_hana} agent plugin, which uses the instance's systemReplicationStatus.py tool to retrieve information from SAP HANA instances. To make this check work, you have to deploy the {sap_hana} agent plugin on a host.

 It uses the output from the systemReplicationStatus.py CLI tool of the SAP HANA instance.

 The check is not configurable.

item:
 The SAP HANA instance.

inventory:
 One service per instance is created if the instance is replicated.
